{"tid":89481,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不如叫地鐵整埋塊關愛板俾你班仆街廢老啦","createTime":"2017-01-21T11:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T05:50:44.000Z","uid":30037,"like":435,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"604b6c8c7df9779fd85a25c38d57bb54bea0e6c2","tid":89481,"uid":30037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:10:24.000Z","msg":"話說我今日搭地鐵，我就企係塊板前面<br />\n<br />\n有個阿婆係黃大仙上車，見到無位坐<br />\n就企正係我前面<br />\n想我俾塊板佢挨下，我就緊係唔撚理佢<br />\n點知個仆街阿婆出口術<br />\n話 後生仔阿婆咁老無位坐，讓個位俾阿婆挨下都得掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就唔理佢繼續，話撚知佢<br />\n點解佢發惡話 依家d後生都唔知係學校學咩嘅，尊敬老人家都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我即刻無名火起<br />\n大大聲屌佢話 我學校有教我大笨象嘅故事 就話呢d大笨象知自己就死，就會死埋一二邊，唔會阻撚住個地球轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢即刻無聲出 過咗陣係彩虹落咗車 <br />\n唔知係唔係受我啟發，死上大帽山唔阻住地球轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab89ce5bc11bd43ccaa3eeef9a426038186cdeb0","tid":89481,"uid":39938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23db4a04cbb8c2ae228b0dd910c71087151318db","tid":89481,"uid":69233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:12:21.000Z","msg":"Ching ho ball"},{"pid":"6ee6a11eaaa2cf4dd3f3b91114329392473aabae","tid":89481,"uid":30037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:16:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打擊廢老 你我有責"},{"pid":"c7c947212af9e74336e1850913e